column5: What an ungodly hour!  Vehicle is packed, hope to make the park office by 7 am, early reports by the advance troops are good, weather forecast is excellent.  Pictures and lies on my return.
good luck and enjoy,look forward to pics
The Best of Luck to ya Bubba! Hope ya catch a Big'un!!!  We Love the lies and Pics!!!  ... loosen off on your drag just a tad...
Have a great time Doug and make sure you post a report. I'm heading up next week.  Mike
